Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.85,0:00:44.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谎言的代价是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is the cost of lies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是它会被错当成真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not that we'll mistake them for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.44,0:00:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的危险是  如果我们听了太多谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The real danger is that if we hear enough lies,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会再无法分辨出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}then we no longer recognize the truth at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时我们要怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What can we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能抛弃追寻真相的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What else is left but to abandon even the hope of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而满足于编造的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and content ourselves instead with stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.46,0:01:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这些故事里  我们不关心英雄是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In these stories, it doesn't matter who the heroes are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只想知道  该责怪谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All we want to know is: who is to blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\pos(194.4,78.934)\blur10\fad(3000,0)\c&HF9FEFF&}莫斯科\N\N\N\N\N{\fs20}1988年4月26日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这则故事里  安纳托利·迪亚特洛夫被怪罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In this story, it was Anatoly Dyatlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.59,0:01:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是最佳选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个自大讨厌的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}An arrogant, unpleasant man,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.51,0:01:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那晚的负责人  是他下了令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he ran the room that night, he gave the orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他没有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少  没有身居高位的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or, at least, not important ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  迪亚特洛夫被判在劳改营\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And now Dyatlov will spend the next ten years
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.62,0:01:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服刑十年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in a prison labor camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  这个刑罚并不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course, that sentence is doubly unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有比他罪行更深重的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There were far greater criminals than him at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而就迪亚特洛夫的确犯的罪而言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And as for what Dyatlov did do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也不该被判服刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the man doesn't deserve prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他该被判死刑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He deserves death.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他被判了十年  罪名是"管理不善罪"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But instead, ten years for "criminal mismanagement."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那什么意思啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道  也无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one knows. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是  对于他们来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does matter is that, to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义已得伸张\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}justice was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你瞧  对于他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because, you see, to them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的世界  是正常的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a just world is a sane world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但切尔诺贝利事件毫无正常可言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was nothing sane about Chernobyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里发生的事  后来发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happened there, what happened after,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是我们做的补救  那一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}even the good we did, all of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都...是疯狂的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}all of it... madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已说出了我知道的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I've given you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们当然会否认\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll deny it, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一向如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会尽力而为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know you'll try your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192.5,161.6)\fn方正大黑_GBK\fs45\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur8\fad(2000,2000)\c&HD3FFFE&}切尔诺贝利\N{\fn方正兰亭中黑简体\fs18}第一集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs29\b1\bord1\shad0\3c&H364845&\blur10\fad(3000,0)\c&HF9FEFF&\pos(192.96,78.934)}苏联乌克兰  普里皮亚季\N\N\N\N\N{\fs25}两年零一分钟前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柳德米拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lyudmilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪亚特洛夫同志  迪亚特洛夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Dyatlov! Comrade Dyatlov!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽轮机大厅着火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a fire in the turbine hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汽轮机大厅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The turbine hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制系统水箱  氢气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The control system tank. Hydrogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和托普特诺夫  你俩白痴把水箱炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You and Toptunov, you morons blew the tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是的  -现在是紧急情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, that's not-- - This is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人保持冷静  我们首先要...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everyone stay calm. Our first priority is--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爆炸了  -我们知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's exploded! - We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基莫夫  在冷却反应堆芯了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Akimov, are we cooling the reactor core?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已关闭反应堆  但控制棒仍在运行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We shut it down, but the control rods are still active.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有完全插入  我已切断离合了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're not all the way in, I disengaged the clutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试用备用控制台切断伺服系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Try and disconnect the servos from the standby console.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩  去启动备用泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You two, get the backup pumps running.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要水流过堆芯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need water moving through the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那才是最重要的  -堆芯没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- That is all that matters. - There is no core.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸了  堆芯爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It exploded, the core exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他吓傻了  把他带出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's in shock. Get him out of here.
