Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今晚不值班啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not on call tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们调集了所有人  军事和民用消防局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're bringing everybody in, military and civil.
