Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次火情很严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但看起来不对劲  那颜色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it doesn't look right, the color.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普拉维克说他们可能打开了泛光灯什么的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pravik says he thinks they're shining floodlights or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那如果有什么化学物质呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what if there are chemicals?
