Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题出在屋顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The problem's the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面铺着沥青  所以会烧上一晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's covered in tar, so it's gonna burn all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且会臭得要命  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and it'll stink like hell. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是最糟的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's the worst of it.
