Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是打仗了吗  -放射性剂量仪在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Is it war? - Where's the dosimeter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这...这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here... Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在轰炸吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are they bombing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这他妈怎么回事  3.6伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What the fuck is this? It's 3.6 roentgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是仪表上限  精度高的锁在保险柜里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's as high as it goes. The good one's locked in a safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't have a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦列拉...你的脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Valera... your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去循环泵室找霍登楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm going to find Khodemchuk in the pump room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...留在这\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You... here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找沙申诺克  他在604室  去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get Shashenok. He's in 604. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得让大家都出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to get everyone out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去反应堆大厅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to get to the reactor hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-电梯坏了  -上两层然后穿过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- The lift's destroyed. - Up two flights and across.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好  -你们去那干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Right. - Why are you going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.95,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看见霍登楚克了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you seen Khodemchuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-没有  维克多在哪  -还在循环泵室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. Where's Viktor? - Still in the pump room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这待着  我一会回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stay here. I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Viktor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Viktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.95,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Viktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多  我带你出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Viktor. I'm gonna get you out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能站起来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can you stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍登楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Khodemchuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找霍登楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get Khodemchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用另一个控制面板插入了控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I dropped the control rods from the other panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-它们还在外头呢  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- They're still up. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只插入了三分之一  我也不知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They're still only a third of the way in, I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派了实习生下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I already sent the trainees
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到反应堆大厅手动插入控制棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}down to the reactor hall to lower them by hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,循环泵那边呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about the pumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联系不上霍登楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't get through to Khodemchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电话坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The lines are down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他妈的电话  去他妈的霍登楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck the phones and fuck Khodemchuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-循环泵开了吗  -斯托利楚克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Are the pumps on or not? - Stolyarchuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的控制面板失效了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My control panel's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着联系电工了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I tried calling for the electricians.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不关心什么面板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't give a shit about the panel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要给反应堆芯通水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need water in my reactor core!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.78,0:15:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到下面去  确保循环泵都开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get down there and make sure those pumps are on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放射量有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What does the dosimeter say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3.6伦琴  但那是仪表上限\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}3.6 roentgen, but that's as high as the meter--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3.6  不好也不坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}3.6-- not great, not terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的操作没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We did everything right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(0,0)\pos(192.5,152)}凌晨1点30分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  把这都接上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You, connect those hooks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动水泵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get the pumps going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.98,0:17:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从下往上灭火  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're working bottom to top. Go in fast.
