Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-瓦西里  这是什么  -不知道  米沙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Hey, Vasily, what's this? - I don't know, Misha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别瞎摆弄了  把这些都接上  快来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't fuck around with it. Hook these up, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尝到金属味儿了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you taste metal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嗯  那是什么  -我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yeah, what is that? - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阀门  米沙  开阀门  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The valves, Misha! The valves, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开阀门  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The valves! Come on!
