Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要到铁路桥上  那边看得更清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going to the railroad bridge to get a better look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正警报声这么大  谁都睡不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not like anyone can sleep with all the sirens.
