Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This kind of explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,标高71米处的控制水箱有100立方米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the control tank on 71, it's 100 cubic meters.
