Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要医生  有人吗  -他脑子不清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I need a medic! Anyone! - He's delusional.
