Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.18,0:23:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给水受到轻度污染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The feedwater is mildly contaminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会没事的  这还不是最糟的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll be fine. I've seen worse.
