Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要电工  机械师  需要人手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need electricians, mechanics, we need bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.55,0:23:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要我说几遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How many times do I have to say it?
