Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  迪亚特洛夫同志\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Comrade Dyatlov.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.17,0:24:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(1500,0)\pos(192.5,152)}凌晨1点50分
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.09,0:24:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你情况很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're doing fine.
