Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.75,0:25:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-楼下怎么样  医生  -很安静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- How's it downstairs, doctor? - Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.65,0:25:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一向如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Always is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.64,0:25:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时候只有婴儿的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing at this hour but babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.16,0:25:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  我曾经连续两天没有睡觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, I once went two days without sleep?
