Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.85,0:25:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我跟你说过这个故事吗  -说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Did I ever tell you that story? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.39,0:25:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这里暂时不需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, I won't need you in here for a while.
