Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.27,0:25:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是说消毒剂吗  -不  是片剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You mean disinfectant? - No, pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.57,0:25:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院有碘片吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Does the hospital stock iodine pills?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.49,0:25:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碘片  我们为什么会有碘片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Iodine pills? Why would we have iodine pills?
