Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.73,0:27:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是什么原因  最重要的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever the cause, the important thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.70,0:27:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我都没...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that neither you nor I--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:23.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(1500,0)\pos(192.5,152)}凌晨2点30分
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.32,0:27:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜安全测试失败了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I take it the safety test was a failure?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.03,0:28:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-情况已经被我们控制住了  -控制住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- We have the situation under control. - Under control?
