Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.32,0:28:08.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把这件事告诉中央委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have to tell the Central Committee about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you realize that?
