Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.25,0:29:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个充满氢气的水箱  火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A hydrogen tank, fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.92,0:29:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-反应堆呢  -我们正在采取措施\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Reactor? - We're taking measures to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.00,0:29:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确保有稳定的水流流过堆芯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a steady flow of water through the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-辐射情况呢  -在这里当然没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What about radiation? - Obviously, down here it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.59,0:29:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在反应堆厂房里  有人告诉我是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But in the reactor building, I'm being told
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.05,0:29:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每小时3.6伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}3.6 roentgen per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.39,0:29:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太妙  但也不太糟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, that's not great, but it's not horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.43,0:29:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.23,0:29:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给水的辐射咯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From the feedwater, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.73,0:29:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得限制换班时间到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll have to limit shifts
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.82,0:29:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每六小时一换  但除此之外...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to six hours at a time, but otherwise...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.86,0:29:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剂量测定员要定期检查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The dosimetrists should be checking regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.45,0:29:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们用保险柜里的高精度仪表\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have them use the good meter from the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.33,0:29:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我去打给马瑞因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right. I'll call Maryin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.58,0:29:41.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去叫醒当地的执行委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have them wake up the local executive committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.96,0:29:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上头随时会有命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There'll be orders coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.72,0:29:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-给  -不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Here. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.26,0:29:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You sure? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.14,0:29:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得颜色是哪儿来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you think makes the colors?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.39,0:30:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-肯定是燃料  -"肯定是燃料"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's the fuel for sure. - "Oh. It's the fuel for sure"?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.11,0:30:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么  你在火车站拖地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you know about it? You clean floors at a train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.28,0:30:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友尤里在核电站工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My friend, Yuri, works at the power plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.03,0:30:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说那里不点火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says it runs cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.74,0:30:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有气体  没有火  只有原子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No gas, no fire. Just atoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.41,0:30:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里说唯一不能做的事就是靠近燃料\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yuri says the only thing is, you can't walk right up to the fuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.16,0:30:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.64,0:30:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得连续四个小时每小时喝一杯伏特加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a glass of vodka an hour for four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.75,0:30:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤里不是水管工吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Isn't Yuri a plumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.96,0:30:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核电站的水管工  没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}At the nuclear power plant, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.72,0:30:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可真美啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.43,0:30:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.50,0:32:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有烟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.07,0:32:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.99,0:33:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.22,0:34:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在外面已束手无策了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've done all we can from the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.02,0:34:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得上屋顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We need to start making our way to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.57,0:34:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦西里  得把火扑灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vasily! You've gotta put it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.57,0:34:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  同志们  我们往前走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's enough, comrades. We're pushing ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.38,0:34:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧  各位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.76,0:34:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦西里  就在前面  直走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vasily, it's just past, straight up.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.05,0:34:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直上去  往里走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the way up, all the way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.68,0:34:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在进入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah. Going in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.70,0:35:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(1500,0)\pos(192.5,152)}凌晨3点30分
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.08,0:35:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辅助装置呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about the auxiliary?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.20,0:35:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泵全毁了  电子设备也没了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The pumps are gone, electrical's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.08,0:35:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堆芯呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The core?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.59,0:36:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没进去  我也不会进去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I didn't go in there, and I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.63,0:36:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是时候面对...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think it's time we faced--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.42,0:36:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我们必须要把水注入堆芯里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, we have to get water into the core.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.63,0:36:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则堆芯会熔毁的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Otherwise, there'll be a meltdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.34,0:36:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须把阀门打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to open the valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.68,0:36:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-萨沙  -那你想怎么做  鲍里斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Sasha... - What do you want, Boris?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.97,0:36:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是这样  我们死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If it's true, then we're dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.92,0:36:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上百万人都死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a million people are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.85,0:36:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想听这话吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is that what you need to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.77,0:36:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须把阀门打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have to open the valves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.69,0:36:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-手动打开  -手动打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- By hand. - By hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.86,0:36:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阀门的数量  转动阀门的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You know, the number of valves, the amount of time to turn them,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.82,0:36:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可要在里面待上几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you're talking about hours in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.07,0:36:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那就帮帮我们吧  -帮你们做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Then help us. - Help you do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.20,0:36:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把水抽进沟里吗  那里什么都没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pump water into a ditch? There's nothing there!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.46,0:36:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德  我求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leonid, I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.64,0:36:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不在的时候  看着点仪表板\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Watch the panel while we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.39,0:36:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.77,0:36:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.48,0:37:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜这就是他们这么早召集我们的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I guess we know why they called us in early.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.75,0:37:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人说发生了什么事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is anyone saying what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.88,0:37:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们之前在对汽轮机进行安全测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were running the safety test on the turbines,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果炸毁了控制系统水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}blew the control system tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.47,0:37:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It doesn't make sense to me either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.56,0:37:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是有人搞破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What about sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.77,0:37:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.31,0:37:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尼考夫  布卡诺夫要我们用精度高的剂量计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sitnikov! Bryukhanov wants us to use the good dosimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.81,0:37:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但剂量计在保险箱里  我们找不到钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's in the safe, and we can't find the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.73,0:37:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在2号厂房里  难道还没...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's in Building 2. Hasn't--?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.20,0:37:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.00,0:38:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs25\b1\bord0\shad0\3c&H364845&\fad(1500,0)\pos(192.5,152)}凌晨5点20分
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.21,0:38:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们  欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gentlemen, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.71,0:38:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请  随便坐吧  很多座位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, uh, find a seat. Plenty of room.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.88,0:38:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉这么晚把你们叫过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I apologize for the lateness of the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.72,0:38:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心  这个地方很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rest assured, we are all very safe down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个庇护所\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We built this shelter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.93,0:38:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是建来抵挡美国核攻击的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to withstand a nuclear attack by the Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.31,0:38:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我觉得我们应该没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so I think we'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.56,0:38:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所见  刚发生了一次事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As you can see, we have experienced an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.90,0:38:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个大型控制水箱出现故障\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A large control tank malfunctioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.61,0:38:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导致4号反应堆厂房发生损坏  并引发火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}damaging reactor Building 4 and starting a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.61,0:38:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立即就上报马瑞因副书记了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, I have spoken directly to Deputy Secretary Maryin.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.24,0:38:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马瑞因上报了弗罗里谢夫副局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Maryin spoke to Deputy Chief Frolyshev,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.74,0:38:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗罗里谢夫上报了中央委员会委员多尔基\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Frolyshev to Central Committee member Dolgikh,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.87,0:38:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多尔基上报了戈尔巴乔夫总书记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Dolgikh to General Secretary Gorbachev.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.88,0:38:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.05,0:38:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为中央委员会极其尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because the Central Committee has the greatest respect
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.72,0:38:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普里皮亚季执行委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}for the work of the Pripyat Executive Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.72,0:39:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要求我如实对你们汇报情况  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they have asked me to brief you on matters as they stand, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.14,0:39:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先事故已经得到控制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}First, the accident... is well under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次  因为苏联在核工业方面的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And second, because the efforts of the Soviet nuclear industry
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.32,0:39:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,属于国家机密\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are considered key state secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.36,0:39:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我们要确保这起事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}it is important that we ensure that
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.41,0:39:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不产生任何负面影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}this incident has no adverse consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.04,0:39:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为避免恐慌  中央委员会已下令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, to prevent a panic, the Central Committee have ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.17,0:39:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向普里皮亚季派遣一支宪兵队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a detachment of military police to Pripyat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.96,0:39:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特遣队有多大规模\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How large of a detachment?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.13,0:39:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两千到四千人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Between two and four thousand men.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.43,0:39:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么  会有多危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's really going on here? How dangerous is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.93,0:39:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有轻微的辐射  但只在工厂范围内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's mild radiation, but it's limited to the plant itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.39,0:39:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  不对  -你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, it isn't. - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.65,0:39:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也看到了外面有人在呕吐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You saw men outside vomiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.73,0:39:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也看到了有人被烧伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You saw men with burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.36,0:39:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辐射情况比他们说的要严重得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's more radiation than they're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.95,0:39:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有我们的妻子  我们的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have wives here, we have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.24,0:40:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我们应该安排全镇撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I say we evacuate the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.54,0:40:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gentlemen--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.91,0:40:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托  我妻子也在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, please. My wife is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.17,0:40:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果普里皮亚季不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you think I would keep her in Pripyat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.17,0:40:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会把她留在这吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if it wasn't safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.79,0:40:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布卡诺夫  空气都在发光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bryukhanov, the air is glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.63,0:40:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是切伦科夫效应  是正常现象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Cherenkov effect. Completely normal phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.63,0:40:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs16\bord0\fn微软雅黑\b0\pos(374,247)}粒子在媒质中传播速度超过媒质中光速时产生的辐射效应
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.84,0:40:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有一点辐射都会发生这种现象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It can happen with minimal radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.06,0:40:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好奇你们中有多少人知道这个地方的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wonder how many of you know the name of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.28,0:40:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我们都叫它"切尔诺贝利"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We all call it "Chernobyl," of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.32,0:40:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它的真名是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What is its real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.41,0:40:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉基米尔·伊里奇·列宁核电站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Vladimir I. Lenin Nuclear Power Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.96,0:40:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.38,0:40:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗拉基米尔·伊里奇·列宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Vladimir I. Lenin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.22,0:41:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚他会为你们感到十分自豪的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how proud he would be of you all tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.98,0:41:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是你  年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Especially you, young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.27,0:41:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你们对人民的关切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and the passion you have for the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.98,0:41:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这不是成立国家政府唯一目的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For is that not the sole purpose of the apparatus of the State?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.78,0:41:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时候  我们会忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes, we forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.03,0:41:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候  我们沦为恐惧的牺牲品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sometimes, we fall prey to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.41,0:41:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们对苏联社会主义的信仰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But our faith in Soviet socialism
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.42,0:41:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终将得到回报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}will always be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.88,0:41:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府告诉我们这里的情况并不危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now, the State tells us the situation here is not dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.51,0:41:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同志们  要有信心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have faith, comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.72,0:41:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府告诉我们要避免恐慌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The State tells us it wants to prevent a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.43,0:41:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.36,0:41:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  当人们看到警察  他们会害怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's true, when the people see the police, they will be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.90,0:42:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根据我的经验\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But it is my experience
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.11,0:42:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当人们提出一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that when the people ask questions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己不利的问题时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that are not in their own best interest,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.66,0:42:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该有人告诉他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they should simply be told
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.50,0:42:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把心思放在工作上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to keep their minds on their labor
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.87,0:42:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将国家的问题留给国家解决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and leave matters of the State to the State.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.51,0:42:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们封锁城市\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We seal off the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.55,0:42:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不许离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.01,0:42:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断电话线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And cut the phone lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.47,0:42:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防消息的误传\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Contain the spread of misinformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.85,0:42:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要防止人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is how we keep the people
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.52,0:42:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏自己的劳动成果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from undermining the fruits of their own labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.90,0:42:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  同志们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, comrades...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.87,0:42:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都将因今晚的所作所为受到奖赏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}we will all be rewarded for what we do here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.25,0:42:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是我们发光发热的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is our moment to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.18,0:43:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.99,0:43:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尼考夫同志来见总工程师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Comrade Sitnikov to see the Chief Engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.46,0:43:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.22,0:43:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我派剂量测定员进入反应堆厂房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I sent my dosimetrists into the reactor building.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.81,0:43:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保险箱中那个大型的剂量计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The large dosimeter from the safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.26,0:43:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最大测量值为一千伦琴的那个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the one with the 1,000-roentgen capacity--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.14,0:43:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,测量读数是多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What was the number?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.85,0:43:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There was none.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.44,0:44:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剂量计一开启就烧坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The meter burned out the second it was turned on.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.90,0:44:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不出所料  -瞧  这就是莫斯科干的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It's typical. - See? This is what Moscow does.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.32,0:44:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我们送来垃圾设备  还问我们哪里出了错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sends us shit equipment, then wonders why things go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.95,0:44:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从军事消防局找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We found another dosimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.45,0:44:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个剂量计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from the military fire department.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它最大测量值只有二百伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It only goes to 200 roentgen,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.66,0:44:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总比小那个的强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but it's better than the small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.71,0:44:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.58,0:44:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它爆表了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It maxed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.67,0:44:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二百伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two hundred roentgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.80,0:44:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在耍什么花招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What game are you playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.80,0:44:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我让他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I--I-- I asked him,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.22,0:44:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他测了好几次  他是我最好的测量员了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he took multiple measurements, he's my best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.26,0:44:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是个故障剂量计  你在浪费我们的时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's another faulty meter. You're wasting our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.81,0:44:35.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我检测了控制水箱附近的读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I checked the meter against the control.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.85,0:44:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么回事  你怎么能从爆炸后的水箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's wrong with you? How'd you get that number
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.15,0:44:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流出的给水中测到这种读数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}from feedwater leaking from a blown tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.98,0:44:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是不可能  -那你在说些什么玩意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You don't. - Then what the fuck are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.37,0:44:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.20,0:44:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我围着4号厂房的外围走了一圈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I walked around the exterior of Building 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.83,0:45:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为地上的碎砖瓦中有石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think there's graphite on the ground in the rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.09,0:45:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有看到石墨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't see graphite.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.76,0:45:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我看到了  -你没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I did. - You didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.63,0:45:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没看到  因为根本没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You didn't! Because it's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.64,0:45:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.18,0:45:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是堆芯  怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you suggesting the core... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.77,0:45:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Exploded?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.48,0:45:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.58,0:45:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尼考夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sitnikov.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.74,0:45:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一个核工程师  我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a nuclear engineer, so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.41,0:45:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我解释下RBMK型反应堆的堆芯怎么会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please tell me how an RBMK reactor core explodes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.79,0:45:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是熔毁  是爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a meltdown, an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.97,0:45:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很乐意听听\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd love to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.18,0:45:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我解释不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.51,0:45:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是蠢货吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.18,0:45:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是  -那你怎么解释不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No. - Then why can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.44,0:46:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.98,0:46:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白它为什么会爆炸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't see how it could explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.90,0:46:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但它的确爆炸了  -够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- But it did. - Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.15,0:46:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去通风厂房楼顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll go up to the vent block roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.74,0:46:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那可以直接看到4号厂房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}From there you can look right down into reactor Building 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.03,0:46:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要亲眼看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll see it with my own... my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.84,0:46:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.01,0:46:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警卫  警卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guards! Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.80,0:46:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他去医生那里或去医院  给他必要的治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Get him to the medic or the hospital! Whatever he needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.32,0:46:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给水  他整晚都在那周围\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's the feedwater. Been around it all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.87,0:46:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.83,0:47:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.71,0:47:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-去通风厂房楼顶  汇报你看到的东西  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Go to the vent block roof and report back what you see. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.63,0:47:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  我不去  -你当然要去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- No, I won't do that. - Of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.60,0:47:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会有事的  放心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll be fine. You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.35,0:47:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.10,0:48:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.15,0:48:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.62,0:48:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leonid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.91,0:48:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列尼德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leonid.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.71,0:48:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部打开  明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all the way, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.80,0:48:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部打开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All the way open.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.64,0:48:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.94,0:48:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好对不起的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's nothing to be sorry for.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.07,0:48:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了  我们的操作没有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I told you, we did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.87,0:49:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但肯定有问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.60,0:52:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.60,0:52:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-瓦列利·列加索夫吗  -是我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Valery Legasov? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.68,0:52:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是库尔恰托夫原子能研究所研究所的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are the Legasov who is the First Deputy Director
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.02,0:52:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一副所长列加索夫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}of the Kurchatov Institute of Atomic Energy?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.81,0:53:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是我  你是...  -我是鲍里斯·谢比纳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I am. Who am I--? - This is Boris Shcherbina,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.44,0:53:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长理事会的副主席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Deputy Chairman of the Council of Ministers
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.57,0:53:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,及燃料与能源局局长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and head of the Bureau for Fuel and Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.69,0:53:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利核电站发生了一起事故\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's been an accident at the Chernobyl Nuclear Power Plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.87,0:53:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多严重\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.66,0:53:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不严重  无需担忧  起火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No. No need to panic. There was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.58,0:53:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分火势已被扑灭  系统控制水箱爆炸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's mostly put out. The system control tank exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.87,0:53:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制系统水箱  那堆芯呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Control system tank. And the core?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.00,0:53:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已下令持续供水冷却\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've ordered them to continuously pump water.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.38,0:53:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了  有污染吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, I see. Any contamination?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.17,0:53:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻度污染  核电站厂长布卡诺夫说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's mild. The plant manager, Bryukhanov, is reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.88,0:53:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每小时3.6伦琴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}3.6 roentgen per hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.68,0:53:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还挺严重  你们应该撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's actually significant. You should evacuate the sur--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.89,0:53:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是RBMK反应堆的专家  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're an expert on RBMK reactors, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.81,0:53:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-对  我研究过  -米哈伊尔·戈尔巴乔夫总书记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Yes, I've studied-- - General Secretary Gorbachev has appointed
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.98,0:53:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设立了一个委员会处理事故  你也是其中一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a committee to manage the accident. You're on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.36,0:53:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天下午两点集合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We'll convene at two this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.61,0:53:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么晚  不好意思  但你不觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That late? Forgive me, but don't you think
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.74,0:53:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鉴于辐射的强度  应该...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}given the amount of radiation that it would be--
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.28,0:53:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列加索夫  你在委员会的职责是回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Legasov, you're on this committee to answer direct questions
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.04,0:53:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何与RBMK反应堆有关的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}about the function of an RBMK reactor
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.54,0:54:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘若有人提问的话  仅此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if they should happen to arise. Nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.75,0:54:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝非参与决策制定  你明白了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Certainly not policy. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.38,0:54:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我无意...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, of course. I didn't mean to-- -
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.22,0:58:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴地汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm pleased to report
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.41,0:59:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切尔诺贝利的情况已稳定了下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that the situation in Chernobyl is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.85,0:59:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就辐射而言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In terms of radiation,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.39,0:59:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被告知辐射量相当于一次胸透\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm told it's the equivalent of a chest X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.32,0:59:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.73,0:59:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大火释放的辐射量近乎是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The fire is giving off nearly twice the radiation
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.99,0:59:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,广岛原子弹的两倍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}released by the bomb in Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.86,0:59:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会一直燃烧  散布毒素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It will burn and spread its poison
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.41,0:59:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到杀死整片大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}until the entire continent is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.33,0:59:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\t(\fscx105\fscy105)\pos(192.5,178.667)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑简体\fs38\b0\bord0\fsp4\shad0\blur7\t(22,529,\blur0)\fad(0,0)\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H8FA7B4&}《切尔诺贝利》\N{\fs17\c&HFFFFFF&}剧情预告
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.34,0:59:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉士兵们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell our soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.05,0:59:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"务必快速行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You will need to move quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.38,0:59:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you will need to move carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.80,0:59:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们人生中最重要的90秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These are the most important 90 seconds of your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.56,0:59:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们长寿健康"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish you good health and long life."
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.23,0:59:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为苏联服务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I serve the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.44,0:59:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为苏联服务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I serve the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.86,0:59:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为苏联服务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I serve the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.04,0:59:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家的官方立场是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The official position of the state
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.62,1:00:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏联是不会发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is that a global nuclear catastrophe
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.96,1:00:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全球性灾难事故的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}is not possible in the Soviet Union.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.04,1:00:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\t(\fscx105\fscy105)\pos(192.5,167.147)}{\fn方正兰亭中黑简体\fs38\b0\bord0\fsp4\shad0\blur0)\fad(0,500)\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H8FA7B4&}切尔诺贝利

